        <Parent_String>economic and financial functions [300069733], functions by general context [300069727], functions (activities) [300138088], Functions (hierarchy name) [300054593], Activities Facet [300264090]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
